 *  - Fully cross-platform.
 *  - Optional horizontal mode.
 *  - Configurable viewability callbacks.
 *  - Header support.
 *  - Footer support.
 *  - Separator support.
 *  - Pull to Refresh.
 *  - Scroll loading.
 *
 * If you need section support, use [`<SectionList>`](/react-native/docs/sectionlist.html).
 *
 * Minimal Example:
 *
 *     <FlatList
 *       data={[{key: 'a'}, {key: 'b'}]}
 *       renderItem={({item}) => <Text>{item.key}</Text>}
 *     />
